{"tid":648641,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[大陸婆] 朱晨麗騷撩人水著 搞到網民一地鼻血","createTime":"2018-04-30T23:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T10:28:47.000Z","uid":82917,"like":17,"dislike":216,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"caceaa4fd23035f314100c55c59f0f9ff8accaa8","tid":648641,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T23:17:41.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】星期一，朱晨麗於社交平台派福利，今日她先貼了一張於峇里島旅遊時泳照，微側身單手撥髮甫士，大騷巨胸纖腰，留言：「用微笑面對每一天！來，深呼吸放鬆一下吧」！<br />\n<br />\n　　由於網民反應奇佳，朱晨麗再貼多幾張不同甫士的泳照，更留言：「送多張俾（畀）努力奮鬥的你」，搞到好多網民謂一地鼻血；貼最後一張時說：「霸住你地嘅屏幕唔好意思，保證係最後一張了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對波成個osim按頸個舊野咁，又蝗味濃，你屌埋我個份<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/071722_8f8ec9ca74cda07cbc5a197a95444fd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F071722_8f8ec9ca74cda07cbc5a197a95444fd6.png&h=65e132d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/071726_c2dc4c604aef36a1f79c464f4971d62a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F071726_c2dc4c604aef36a1f79c464f4971d62a.png&h=704fa834&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3fb6fd631cfd26b32c243964ea68c577125bb9e","tid":648641,"uid":82917,"like":27,"dislike":184,"score":-157,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T23:18:16.000Z","msg":"唔洗召喚老母住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/071814_d81103445ced458f07bec35995409c6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F071814_d81103445ced458f07bec35995409c6a.png&h=2dc7bae